                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote>
                        <p>Youth in profile, left foot advanced, wearing an oliver wreath with fruit
                           and leaves and holding up two pomegranates in his raised left hand. His
                           flexed right arm and hand (with wrist muscles preserved) held
                           an anaryballos suspended from a leather strap.</p>
                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote>
                        <p>tongues in low relief on the shoulder of the aryballos</p>
                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote>
                        <p>lotus flowers and buds around the body in low relief on the aryballos</p>
                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote>
                        <p>crescents in low relief radiating from the bottom of the aryballos </p>
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
